{"type": "article", "id": 10236, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-06-01T07:59:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 513, "name": "虚拟现实"}, {"id": 3533, "name": "容器"}, {"id": 566, "name": "手机"}, {"id": 10902, "name": "插板"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 10903, "name": "Lenovo"}, {"id": 10904, "name": "Lina"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235701ZAY36eSxPlpgQBfV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tShapes Bundle by Visibility\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t纽约设计工作室 Visibility 与同样来自纽约的服饰品牌 Outdoor Voice 联合推出了一套家用健身产品“Shapes Bundle”，这个系列包括一个阻力带，一个木材瑜伽块，一个三角形软木块，一个 12 边的桦木辊和一个毛毡毯，通过不同产品的排列组合，可以配合不同的运动类型，进行力量训练和瑜伽训练。这是<a href=\"http://vsby.co/\" target=\"_blank\">工作室的官方主页</a>，点击可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071321471xMlrufQsUZ6d4VS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132147dqG4QcxVYb9zhreO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132148ZRTB2QdtXiO7CAxp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071321487R2CsZBdpkO5yAwc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132149C6d4A9sPY8nkUv1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68854167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132149S0sKYpFdNHhlT5Mk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50729167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132150eZQNgS9iFqyHz0sM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62395833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132150e5L3sJXwNMVFYcTC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132150fpWB8QDzwRNMFt3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tPortiko by Bluelounge\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t美国设计工作室 Bluelounge 最近推出了一款叫做 “Portiko” 的便携式插板，小巧的插板上在两侧各有一个插座和一个 USB 端口，两侧的分布避免了电源线缠绕在一起，而插板的线有 6 米长，满足多种情形下的需求。目前产品有白色和蓝色两种颜色可选，售价 25 美元。<a href=\"http://www.bluelounge.com/us/portiko\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132151mUXwAqyJbO4vEaV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132151TdYw1kGCOz2yfUu0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071321522DPJ1xgiTydBKwGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tKeywest by Lenovo\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t联想最近在 TechWorld 大会推出了一款 Smart Cast 智能投影手机，不仅具备墙面投影模式，还可以把任意平面变成触摸屏，随时随地进行操作和分享。手机号称是业界首款免对焦激光智能投影手机。不过，目前产品还未进入量产。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132152WUnTCidtAGhk5ox0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132153R4PFO0c8mvfpqt2u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tMoon Chaise Lounge by Lina\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是斯洛维尼亚家具品牌 Lina 推出的一个多功能躺椅，这个叫做 “Moon Chaise Lounge”（月亮躺椅）的作品采用模块化的设计，通过不同元素的组合，可以形成桌子，椅子，沙发等，颜色靓丽鲜明。此外，软垫可拆卸、可水洗，不用的时候可以方便地堆在一边塞进角落里面。目前产品售价 176 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.lovethesign.com/uk/lina/moon-chaise-longue\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132153pHXUV32mlTcPdYMA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132153gEk8Oy6tlwpoGUqF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132154P1WNFjbewi9rDSZJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54767726\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132154bFp3SZTJIExcedXL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071321552YW8JDIKtMefGoVN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132155kDfK7lmXNGauMy0R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87286064\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tDior Eyes by Dior\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tDior 最近推出了虚拟现实设备 “Dior Eyes”，用户戴上它，可以身临其境地去 Dior 时装秀的后台近距离进行观看，包括化妆师为模特化妆的过程，模特上台前在做什么等全方位的后台景象，“Dior Eyes ” 将于今年 6 月正式发布，将会在全球部分精品店内提供产品体验。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132155Q5hez3RBkgjZI9Ty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132156QkD12lrVjIPcUOSn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071321565mdvwIyaJCqZKH9M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58312958\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132157Oj1Ue2A0PzblDBrq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071321576EzVCID1TxR2iwpH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132157w20dzmFtXLchAKEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tFlaws by Marie Liebhardt\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t法国设计师 Marie Liebhardt 推出了一套容器作品，命名为“残缺”，一套为金属材质，一套为瓷器材质，其共同点在于在产品的表面通过纹理的设计和制作，营造出“残缺”的效果。其设计灵感来自于城市中墙壁和街道等随着时间的流逝老化后的模样，用作品来表现时间的流逝和光阴的印记。这是<a href=\"http://marieliebhardt.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看他更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071321581j3rkIvGsgucF6RZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132159ZNIAaR2SMCqyniPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132159chV0Bb2WgREwN8rZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132159fTMuBjzVOP3rbogx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132200QAZoligKqhaxDFvH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132201lm0zArJuCjX4a6Sw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66354167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132201EVIg39lepar4kA5M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}